fit=crop\" alt=\"\"></cnx></cnx></div><p><cnx-span>The Galaxy Buds Pro are Samsung’s newest wireless earbuds. They come in Phantom Silver, Phantom Violet, and Phantom Black and are available today for $200. With solid microphones, a slim design, and decent battery life, these earbuds have kept all of the good parts or the Galaxy Buds that have come before them. But what earns them their Pro title are all their extra features.</cnx-span></p><hr></div></div>","author":"John Gruber","siteTitle":"Daring Fireball","siteHash":"fc569638025dadf22a867470f8215f38855cf50e975782a6c989909474292a36","entryHash":"222d57a86fa02cee383d9fc09ebb3952b8d8cd65aecadd8bd3ec7ea89166181e","category":"Tech"}